## 3. Minimal chart files (what interviewers expect you to name)

```text
my-service/
├── Chart.yaml
├── values.yaml
└── templates/
    ├── deployment.yaml
    ├── service.yaml
    └── _helpers.tpl
```

**`deployment.yaml` (idea):**

```yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: {{ include "my-service.fullname" . }}
spec:
  replicas: {{ .Values.replicaCount }}
  template:
    spec:
      containers:
        - name: app
          image: "{{ .Values.image.repository }}:{{ .Values.image.tag }}"
```

