## 9. Commands (Helm day-to-day)

```bash
helm lint ./charts/order
helm template order ./charts/order -f values.prod.yaml   # render locally, no cluster
helm install order ./charts/order -n orders -f values.prod.yaml
helm upgrade --install order ./charts/order -n orders -f values.prod.yaml
helm list -n orders
helm history order -n orders
helm rollback order 3 -n orders
helm dependency update ./platform   # umbrella chart
```

